@NODE 16. "New FileTypes"

      WhatDir doesn't recognize all filetypes! If you have found
    a new fileformat that WhatDir doesn't recognize please send
    me information about this format, as complete information as
    possible. And please send as many as possible diffrent files
    of that format. The BEST would be if you send me the program
    that creates those files!!

      Please also report Bugs and suggestions to make WhatDir even
    better than now. Please correct me if I have classified a file
    wrong! Although it's very easy to make mistakes when I have
    over 500 filetypes to classify.

      Is there a need for an intuition (gadtools) mode in WhatDir?
    Should I make it a shared library? Please write to me and tell me!



